  "remarks": "On 18 March 2014 the Crimean Parliament transferred the seized Crimean assets of a subsidiary of a Ukrainian state-owned gas company to Chernomorneftegaz.\nThe enterprise is thus effectively confiscated by the Crimean ‘authorities’. \nRe-registered on 29 November 2014 as State Unitary Enterprise of the ‘Republic of Crimea’ ‘Chernomorneftegaz’. \nFormerly known as PJSC ‘Chernomorneftegaz’.\nPhone: +7 (3652) 66-70-00 \nPhone: +7 (3652) 66-78-00\nWebsite: http://gas.crimea.ru/\nEmail: office@gas.crimea.ru \nRegistration ID: 1149102099717 (Russia)\nTax ID No.: 9102048801 (Russia); Listing: Listed on 16 June 2017, re-listed 10 Jun 2020 and 29 March 2021 and 10 June 2023",
